INTRODUCTION:
=============
UniverseCore is an open source web framework for mobile platforms. The UniverseCore framework is written in C and is designed to be portable.

COMPILING:
=============
PalmOS and Linux:
make -f <Platform makefile>

or use Codewarrior

MacOS X:
Build from inside of XCode with the UniverseCore project file.

SOURCE:
=============
The source code is available at:

http://www.openmobl.com/

or through the SVN at:

http://www.sf.net/projects/universecore/


